    <text type="note" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-09143"> 
        <body>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when-custom="1792-03-22">1792 г. 22 марта.</date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>
            <p>Пожалуй возвратите <persName ref="people.xml#arn01">Арндту</persName>. <rs ref="people.xml#arn01">Он</rs> в трех местах найдет моих записок, не для внесения в <rs ref="people.xml#arn01">его</rs> сочинение
                <note type="editorial">
                    This note refers to <persName ref="people.xml#arn01">Christian Gottlieb von Arndt</persName>'s work <title xml:lang="de">"Über den Ursprung und die verschiedenartige Verwandtschaft der europäischen Sprachen"</title> that was published in Germany after 1818. However, Catherine knew this work in its first version in French under the title <title xml:lang="fr">"Idées sur l'origine et l'affinité des langues"</title>. (
                    <bibl>
                        <title ref="works.xml#filolz01">Filologicheskie zaniatiia Ekateriny II</title>
                        , <biblScope unit="pp">pp. 440.</biblScope>
                    </bibl>
                    ).
                </note>
                , но <seg xml:lang="fr">comme des reflexions qui me sont venues en lisant. Dites <rs ref="people.xml#arn01">lui</rs> de ma part, que j’ai trouvé son ouvrage très intéressant et que la lecture m’en a amuse. Vous pouvez <rs ref="people.xml#arn01">lui</rs> montrer <ref target="letter-09143">ce billet</ref></seg>.</p>
        </body>
